Package: rwdpa
Title: World Database of Protected Areas
Description: Client for the World Database of Protected Areas.
    Fetching metadata on the areas, fetching shape files for each,
    functions for simplifying polygons, for plotting, and converting
    to WKT to faciltate downstream queries of species occurrence
    data.
Version: 0.0.8.9100
